{"tid":528364,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[宣傳] 失物平台希望幫到有需要既人","createTime":"2018-01-13T16:54:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-19T03:39:27.000Z","uid":104580,"like":33,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"653dbc15a4214727c58f445b4b50350acfb99983","tid":528364,"uid":104580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T16:54:44.000Z","msg":"細佬我因為經歷過唔見左野既痛苦，知道有d野係用錢都未必搵得返<br />\n如果有一個平台能幫到人集合所有失物相關既資料，包括尋人，尋動物，電話<br />\n係最近既lonely christmas 工餘時間同幾個同事寫左個失物app同網站出黎<br />\n希望得到各位巴絲打既推廣，將呢個平台發揚光大<br />\n俾個五星我地／Like 我地facebook專頁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/dPqutp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FdPqutp.jpg&h=95f5a1ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/ZwrBil.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FZwrBil.jpg&h=61950c15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/7aNDkH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2F7aNDkH.png&h=ca561b81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n**至於上架同伺服器費用都係我同幾個同事夾錢維持<br />\n程式內絕無任何廣告，收費，只係一個簡單登記平台<br />\n**只希望香港有更多好人好事發生<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網站：[仍在debug 當中][新年後轉做Https]<br />\n<a href=\"http://findyourlost.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffindyourlost.hk%2F&d=DAvTgABvU1htLMBbKnqBPzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=1d3d6e8d\" target=\"_blank\">http://findyourlost.hk/</a><br />\n手機程式 Android：<br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.findyourlost2.app\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.findyourlost2.app&d=DAvTgABvU1htLMBbKnqBPzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=ce694523\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.findyourlost2.app</a><br />\n手機程式 IPhone：<br />\n<a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/hk/app/findyourlost-%E5%AE%88%E6%9C%9B/id1324895465?mt=8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fapp%2Ffindyourlost-%25E5%25AE%2588%25E6%259C%259B%2Fid1324895465%3Fmt%3D8&d=DAvTgABvU1htLMBbKnqBPzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=ea3b9ffe\" target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/hk/app/findyourlost-%E5%AE%88%E6%9C%9B/id1324895465?mt=8</a><br />\nFacebook:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/FindYourLostHK/?fref=nf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FFindYourLostHK%2F%3Ffref%3Dnf&d=DAvTgABvU1htLMBbKnqBPzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=2fe3ec86\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/FindYourLostHK/?fref=nf</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n賣多個廣告：<br />\n目前有多兩個程式製作中：<br />\n1. 交友app [缺designer中]<br />\n尚欠designer 一名，幫手製作可愛既頭像<br />\n2. 書app [2月份推出]<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有咩任何問題歡迎tg我<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/findyourlost\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ffindyourlost&d=DAvTgABvU1htLMBbKnqBPzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=cd907840\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/findyourlost</a>"},{"pid":"6f5f8135e8c4d41f9b8ecd6fb67ec27f89da3376","tid":528364,"uid":104580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T17:13:16.000Z","msg":"pu<br />\nsh"},{"pid":"9de56c84b14113d36ee31e0070042d46025f79ab","tid":528364,"uid":104580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T17:54:33.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d23d7131a19fc4e6b810195b409d561b24b01b99","tid":528364,"uid":20189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T17:58:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"378a7eccc28d20e34afd50340cbfd09798d29ae9","tid":528364,"uid":104580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T18:01:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/14/020056_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F14%2F020056_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=d4636e5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n遺失熱線界面"},{"pid":"29c80cb018fb4152c6d4e7e97ca14cf6b81e18c3","tid":528364,"uid":40348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T18:23:00.000Z","msg":"idea幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但搵唔到錢"},{"pid":"7f846f04f76d5e155d544fb7203f0bacee5b1575","tid":528364,"uid":104580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29c80cb018fb4152c6d4e7e97ca14cf6b81e18c3","tid":528364,"uid":40348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T18:23:00.000Z","msg":"idea幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但搵唔到錢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T01:37:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我地當初做出黎係諗住幫到人<br />\n打算再整其他app 慢慢黎<br />\n反正用Google Server 每月都係幾十美金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw 多謝你支持，有時間去play store/app store 俾個五星我地"},{"pid":"024fd89fb1a20942b8357d9bede72f7bd31c3914","tid":528364,"uid":104580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T03:47:25.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"eec9e45b7936c0f9e52294578c7190f75faea12e","tid":528364,"uid":104580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T04:00:11.000Z","msg":"我們相信冇人會經常需要尋找失物，但當有一天，<br />\n您拾獲物件想幫人時，又或者丟失東西求助時，<br />\n發現要在不同的渠道報失、尋找。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果你都希望大家可以在同一個平台尋找失物，希望在這一刻就Like 這個Page並且Share比您身邊的朋友。"},{"pid":"1eb22b3043c29d4af12a88c3c5e7f349b279018e","tid":528364,"uid":54324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T04:04:45.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3340f3c0c902aa17d01dbde1d2c5a94f3a6b23e3","tid":528364,"uid":47971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T04:06:00.000Z","msg":"支持 等出書app<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28393bf4b7f4ab4a635574c7d9ac1c070deec3c6","tid":528364,"uid":104580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3340f3c0c902aa17d01dbde1d2c5a94f3a6b23e3","tid":528364,"uid":47971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T04:06:00.000Z","msg":"支持 等出書app<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T04:08:29.000Z","msg":"多謝，依家逐區周圍行收集緊小店既資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有好多功能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cb97545f37bb53fc56b503bc14cde8b3df00d4f","tid":528364,"uid":104580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T04:46:53.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5b5cb3eadca9c882d8613a36f4a3f4b0544a6d9e","tid":528364,"uid":104580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T06:42:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"15e2326adecef330854c9de41e3e3bacb84a1856","tid":528364,"uid":46227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T06:43:23.000Z","msg":"請問除左失左物既人，正常冇失物既普通人點解要裝你個app?"},{"pid":"0d89b88df07c67e4d8c063dc8823e81100836584","tid":528364,"uid":104580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15e2326adecef330854c9de41e3e3bacb84a1856","tid":528364,"uid":